CustomField.description: The Arrow NaviCurve Stylet is supplied preloaded in geometrically compatible 4-6 French Arrow PICCs and is also available as a replacement component in the vent the preloaded Stylet becomes compromised during preparation or use. when using the NaviCure Stylet as a replacement for a NaviCure Stylet previously preloaded in an Arrow PICC, ensure to place the Stylet in the same lumen as Previously loaded
